CODE
====

Pablo Arias (Author)
Marc Lebrun (Author of the original NLBayes for still image denoising)

NOTE: The code is a largely modified version of the NLBayes image denoising
algorithm available here:

Marc Lebrun, Antoni Buades, and Jean-Michel Morel,
Implementation of the "Non-Local Bayes" (NL-Bayes) Image Denoising Algorithm,
Image Processing On Line, 3 (2013), pp. 1–42.
https://doi.org/10.5201/ipol.2013.16


